<br>
Since day 1 of the epic quests, I couldn't understand for the life of me the point of making Quil's cloak a part of the epic. Nor can I understand why Phinny is considered an epic mob for so many classes. <br>
<br>
Not only does the whole rarity factor add in an un-needed difficulty, it doesn't go along with an actual RP storyline. How often does the hero go back and kill the same monster, because it didn't have it's treasure?<br>
<br>
Rare drops as epic items does not make since to me. If it's going to be epic, put it on a hard ass mob and make it drop every time.  <p><center> -- I broke my Flappy's wings --<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=92172">Toxx Wyrmbane 55 Evoker</a>, Heart of Fenris </center></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showMessageRange?topicID=222.topic&start=21&stop=24>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showPrevMessage?topicID=222.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showNextMessage?topicID=222.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=222.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.threadControl?topicID=222.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=222.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerrants.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=222.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="themagicianstowerannouncements">Administrat